{
  "stem": "5795.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] She says, my father's missing.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And so far as I know, many of the Jews were killed.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And their fat was made into soap.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So it took me minutes to convince her this soap is from England.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was coming back, and I-- out of my office, I noticed a lieutenant and a sergeant or a corporal.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I went-- why can't I remember her name?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I say, what?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Who, who are they?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "What are they?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "She said, they're looking for evidence either to acquit or to punish the commandant in the camp where we were liberated.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I gave evidence in favor of the commandant.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Why?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "If it wasn't for him, many of us would have been killed by the-- by the SS inside.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was a, a businessman in the First World War.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Had very, very many friends, Jewish friends.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was too old to, to join the army.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So they gave him this job.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But he couldn't bring himself to murder as the others did.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So from that point of view, I, I gave evidence in his favor.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "What happened, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Then she told me that six girls, who, as they were being marched through the streets going to further-- to the camps, or wherever it was, the civilians used to shoot from their windows.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Six girls were killed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I believe they were buried in the-- in the cemetery.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I said, come on, show me the cemetery.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And at that particular time, the order came-- no British soldier should frat with a German girl.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "The news of the-- of the-- of the horrors of these camps was spread amongst the troops.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And the order was no-- don't frat with these German girls.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
